reviewText: Love Tae Bo and the package came right away without problems

Cover is what I ordered but contents was a totally differnt workout! No return address for order,I was very dissapointed.
I paid for something I didn't order.
It was a replacement from the same tape that was destroyed by my tape player. I going to buy a new DVD/VCR player soon.
This is a good workout, but moves really fast with little or bad instructions. Be prepared to watch it a few times before really being able to keep up.
